title: New Creator: Brian Solis
body:
Name: Brian Solis

Socials: http://www.twitter.com/briansolis
http://www.briansolis.com

Info: Brian Solis is a world-renowned digital anthropologist and futurist. He is also an award-winning author and global keynote speaker. Brian’s research, advisory and presentations humanize the relationship between disruptive innovation and its impact on institutions, markets and societies. He not only helps audiences understand what’s happening and why, he visualizes future trends and inspires people to take leading roles in defining the future they want to see.

Use Cases:
Incorporating coin giveaways and transaction use cases around his writing, keynote speaking, mentorship, and existing paid transaction/subscription programs.

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' will approve Brian with a $1,000 Community Treasury Gift Coin grant.

A 'no' will deny this proposal.
